  "body": "### Component\n\nAnvil\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nAs [documented](https://hardhat.org/hardhat-network/docs/guides/forking-other-networks#resetting-the-fork), calling `hardhat_reset` with empty params disables forking and restores the node to its default state.\r\n\r\nCurrently, doing this in anvil results in `expected params sequence with length 1 but got 0`.\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
